# 10.36: How Does Context Shape Plot Twists? 

Listen [here](http://www.writingexcuses.com/2015/09/06/writing-excuses-10-36-how-does-context-shape-plot-twists/). 

**Prompt:** Unwinding the Twist: Find a plot twist in something that you enjoy, and then backtrack a bit. Take notes. Figure out where the red herrings are. Figure out where the foreshadowing is. Enumerate these, see if thereâ€™s something formulaic that you can learn from.
